Z", "updated_at": "2017-04-17T17:58:23Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/pull/9214#discussion_r111545009", "pull_request_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/tensorflow/tensorflow/pulls/9214", "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR", "_links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.github.com/repos/tensorflow/tensorflow/pulls/comments/111545009"}, "html": {"href": "https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/pull/9214#discussion_r111545009"}, "pull_request": {"href": "https://api.github.com/repos/tensorflow/tensorflow/pulls/9214"}}, "body_html": "<p>This change is needed to fix bazel tests in tensorflow/compiler when jemalloc is enabled. Jemalloc code uses pthread_atfork function in jemalloc.c which gets executed in case of Power but not on x86. To resolve this function, we need jemalloc to be built linking libpthread.</p>", "body_text": "This change is needed to fix bazel tests in tensorflow/compiler when jemalloc is enabled. Jemalloc code uses pthread_atfork function in jemalloc.c which gets executed in case of Power but not on x86. To resolve this function, we need jemalloc to be built linking libpthread."}